casebody.data:
Billy WATKINS, Petitioner
v.
STATE of North Carolina and Tracey Cline, Assistant District Attorney. No. 244P03-12. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2004. Billy Watkins, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, James E. Hardin, Jr., District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 9th day of June 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Durham County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th day of June 2004."
